{
  "stem": "3933.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I put it back there in the-- I was so naive and so stupid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I came back to this [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Kola, ?] there, because I-- I was only-- he told me you can sleep here only one or two nights, Mary-- my brother-- it was-- it should have been-- it wasn't nice of him, but-- well, anyway.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back to Kola.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him about this little bag.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I [INAUDIBLE] to my son is Mama, how-- you, it's being so sensible and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I take this little bag, I could go away in another city and rent a room for this kind of money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, anyway.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't you think he took away a little bit, and it's something you open like a lock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went, he took everything and stole-- he went there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He stole-- he took this little bag.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He gave something to his sister, the one who's in Auschwitz, if she's still alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest of it, he drank it over and chased me out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's when we became-- I became really homeless-- homeless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is a joke.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With this child.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I say, I'm not going to be able anymore to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going to have to go straight to the Gestapo and say, here I am, here we are, both Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Take me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I figure I've got to run away from this city where I was-- there is not written on my forehead that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have to get out of this damned Rowne.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were so many soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was war then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Many soldiers traveling back and forth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know-- so many army men.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
